content:
Optimize your contact center operations using the power of Artificial Intelligence (AI). Effortlessly gauge the sentiment of call conversations. Trigger actions based on signals and keywords detected during a conversation. Turn on AI-generated call summaries for efficient analysis.

Improve customer service and agent training with sentiment analysis of call conversations. Agents and supervisors can view turn-by-turn sentiment alongside the call recording from a previous conversation.

To help your agents during calls, automatically trigger actions based on intelligence signals from your telephony system or keywords mentioned by agents or customers.

To save time and be more attentive during conversations with customers, agents no longer have to take notes and summarize the call conversation. The agent can use Einstein Work Summary to generate a high-quality summary of a voice calls.
title: Automate Contact Center with Artificial Intelligence
